{"tid":1056335,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【傷口灑鹽】胡杏兒「清者自清」被鬧多事 傅嘉莉懶理負評﹕我真心喜歡演戲","createTime":"2019-03-11T06:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T08:32:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6b685a676aac0283dd97bf4eae4b2bbad6e66a6c","tid":1056335,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"傅嘉莉(Kelly)今日突然在Instagram發長文，鬧爆剛剛宣佈離婚的呂慧儀和黃文迪，當年明知「黑甲女」不是她，仍未有為她澄清。<br />\n不過，有不少心水清的網民，卻發現當年呂慧儀是有發文為Kelly澄清，指「她是一個好女孩，大家不要誤會她了，女孩的名聲很重要。」惹來不少網民質疑Kelly抽水，「好心佢啦～人哋離婚都要抽一抽」、「妳都係女人，何必落井下石呢！妳咪一樣搏見報」，「在人家離婚傷口上灑鹽」等等。連有份在Kelly的IG留言「清者自清」的胡杏兒亦遭殃，同樣被人鬧「多事」！<br />\n被網民都洗版式攻擊的Kelly，她午後由IG轉戰Facebook，並上載一張工作相片，說：「為何選擇藝人這工作，我會毫不猶豫地回答，因為我真心喜歡演戲，我可能不是一個成功的藝人，但我會努力做好一位用心的演員。」<br />\n傅嘉莉facebook link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fukaleekelly/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffukaleekelly%2F&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FODrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=1b8938ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fukaleekelly/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190310/large/1552213705_ecb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190310%2Flarge%2F1552213705_ecb1.jpg&h=3e262f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190310/59353056\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190310%2F59353056&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FODrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=6589e0b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190310%2F59353056&h=4d049f87\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190310/59353056</a>"},{"pid":"f32f57aa00ac1abebee47c974e33972f351747c5","tid":1056335,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"